## Summary of Bugs Fixed

| # | Bug | File | Fix |
|---|-----|------|-----|
| 1 | Background scrolls behind open modal | `booking-modal.tsx` | `document.body.style.overflow = "hidden"` on open |
| 2 | No Escape key support | `booking-modal.tsx` | `keydown` event listener |
| 3 | Stale form data on re-open | `booking-modal.tsx` | `handleClose` now resets `formData` |
| 4 | `<input type="hidden" required>` ignored by browsers | `booking-modal.tsx` | Removed; JS guard in `handleSubmit` |
| 5 | `today` recomputed every render | `booking-modal.tsx` | Wrapped in `useMemo` |
| 6 | No phone format validation | `booking-modal.tsx` | Regex `/^0\d{9}$/` + inline error |
| 7 | Expired time slots shown when today selected | `booking-modal.tsx` | Filter `TIME_SLOTS` by current time |
| 8 | Barber required with no "don't care" option | `booking-modal.tsx` | Added "Bất kỳ thợ nào" option |

